                     <listitem>
                        <para>No release notes found.</para>
                     </listitem>
                  </varlistentry>
               </variablelist>
            </sect4>
            <sect4>
               <title>critical</title>
               <variablelist>
                  <varlistentry>
                     <term>193: It happens, that the cluster gets stuck in activating volume groups</term>
                     <listitem>
                        <para>It can happen, that the cluster stucks inside the initrd when trying to
activate lvm volumegroups after cman has been started.

This happens when 3 of nodes are booted at the same time, i.e. without a quorum
disk.</para>
                     </listitem>
                  </varlistentry>
               </variablelist>
            </sect4>
